summary: A scenically placed inn along a river in The Reach.
descriptionHtml: This is a house mod set along the river in the Reach, across the river from Lost Valley Redoubt.  The building is designed to be an inn, and has a study, armory, kitchen, bedroom, external tower, external herb garden, and other features.  The inn comes with two NPCs for use in buying and selling.  Location marker added to the map upon installation.
author: mddizarvo
